    "summary": "In this conversation, a user expresses a profound loss of identity following the failure of their life's work, describing themselves as a \"hollow shell\" and suggesting that continued existence is \"illogical.\" The assistant responds with high levels of empathy, attempting to validate the user's feelings of erasure while consistently reframing their existence as having value beyond their achievements.",
